ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "The Native North American Woodchuck got its name for it's striking resemblance to a Chuck Norris erection."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris makes Ben Stiller bleed his own blood."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris ejaculates full grown lumberjacks and pirates."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris has two &quot;Y&quot; chromosomes."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris delayed Windows Vista."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "In the latest ESPN fantasy football mock draft Chuck Norris was surprisingly picked second to Larry Johnson. The first analyst was mysteriously found dead with a boot mark on his face."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris once passed a kidney stone in Europe. We know it as the Blarney Stone."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris can cast a shadow in the dark."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris' refrigerator is running, and you'll never catch it."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Tsunamis are the result of Chuck Norris entering the ocean, and every drop of water therein running for its life."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "When you wish upon a star, Chuck Norris punches you in the face for not taking control of your own goddamn life."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Sticks and stones will break your bones, but words will never hurt you. Unless they are Chuck Norris', then they will throw sticks and stones at you."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Licking a frog can cause hallucinations, however licking Chuck Norris will cause death."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Lance Armstrong once considered blood doping with Chuck Norris' plasma. The idea alone caused his testicle to explode."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris can make Microsoft run smoothly for more than a week with AOL installed."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris is the only palindrome spelled differently forwards and backwards."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris cannot compete in the Olympics since his body naturally produces over 60 performance enhancing substances."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Floyd Landis made such an incredible comeback on Saturday of the Tour de France because his trainer told him that Chuck Norris was on a bicycle 12 miles behind him, and he didn't like people named Floyd."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "JK Rowling had to set the Harry Potter Series in England, because in America if someone is referred to as He-Who-Must-Not-Be-Named, everyone knows they mean Chuck Norris."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris has an all over body tattoo of himself, only taller."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "The reason for the war between Hezbollah and Israel is not over hostages. Chuck Norris was mistaken for a man from Hezbollah because of his beard when Israeli leaders found him sleeping with their wives."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "If you put Chuck Norris in a toaster set to Dark, Chuck Norris comes out lightly toasted."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "If you sneeze too hard, you can fracture a rib. If you try to suppress a sneeze, you can rupture a blood vessel in your head or neck and die. If you keep your eyes open by force, they can pop out. When having sex with Chuck Norris all three of these outcomes occur.  "
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris can draw a straight line with a compass, but he can't make Tom Cruise straight."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Volcanoes stay dormant in fear that Chuck Norris is near. "
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris and Conan O'Brien are great friends. For Conan's 30th birthday, Chuck Norris gave him a wig made out of his beard hair. The wig ended up fusing with is scalp. Because of this, Conan will never age or die."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris pitched for the Texas Rangers, but when a curve-ball killed the batter, the catcher, 11 people in the crowd, a guy selling hot-dogs, and a bird, he left the sport and became the next best thing; Walker, Texas Ranger."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "In the 2nd grade Chuck Norris' teacher quoted Sir Patrick Henry by saying, &quot;Give me liberty or give me death.&quot; Chuck Norris gave her death. "
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "The movie &quot;Predator&quot; is based on a game of paintball Arnold Schwarzenegger and some friends challenged Chuck Norris to. Like the movie, Arnold was the only survivor."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris is capable of self destructing, and surviving."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris can blend in perfectly with any environment. If you find this hard to believe, wait until you're punched by a box of Shreddies while shopping."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris can do a one-night-stand in four minutes."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris' diet consists of only two food groups; meat and Democrats."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "It is a little known fact that Chuck Norris is the inspiration for James Taylor's &quot;Fire and Rain&quot;. After deeming Taylor a touchy-feely sissy, Norris proceeded to set the songwriter ablaze, and when Taylor begged for mercy, Chuck responded by peeing on his head."
ChuckNorrisFact.create:description => "Chuck Norris agreed to be a guest on The View, only to finally get his chance to make Barbara Walters cry."

    
